# Keep the API image build fast and its layer cache stable. Only the root workspace config,
# packages/shared, and apps/api feed the build; everything else just bloats the context (sent to
# the daemon on every build) and busts the layer cache on changes that don't affect the API.
.git
.github
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.turbo
**/.expo
docs
infra
apps/mobile
apps/admin
*.md
.env
.env.*
